{
  "stem": "10829.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to ride in town on their horses in groups.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I probably am exaggerating, but I don't think there were more than about 10, 12, if it was 15, but it seemed like it was a whole battalion.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't think it was more than about that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used to tear the city, basically, apart.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to take the women or girls and [INAUDIBLE] revenge from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the only object that they had and what they got paid for is how many they can kill, how many can they rape.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to get rewarded for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you can picture-- and I use-- I relate to, which I've seen a lot of the Western towns, you have the cattle men coming in the town, shooting it up and all.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's about what happened to Trochenbrod.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you could almost figure-- well, when it came around Friday night, we used to try to get together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of us used to get split up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For an example, we tried not to be too many in one time, because when they attacked, they would used to kill as many as they can.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The younger girls, like my mother, sister, used to always hide Friday night and Saturday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to hide.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Going back, the-- the-- the city were-- the [INAUDIBLE] where we were, almost every home in Trochenbrod-- I don't think it was an exception-- we had storm windows on the outside.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had hidden cellars or hidden closets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Almost every house did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For example, we used to make leather and all this, and when the-- when the goyim used to know, they used to come and attack you, and they'd steal from you.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
